  <h1>About This BJC Tool</h1>

  <div class="section imei-box">
    <p>
      <strong>BJC Bandlocking Tool</strong> is a mobile-friendly web app designed to make it easy to:
    </p>
    <ul style="text-align: left;">
      <li>Log in to your ZLT S10G router (Admin/User)</li>
      <li>Lock onto specific LTE bands (Band 3, 28, 40, 41)</li>
      <li>Generate valid IMEI numbers for device testing</li>
      <li>Search online using a built-in Google search</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      This tool works offline (for IMEI and UI), and can be packaged into an APK.
    </p>
    <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">
